ZH: 我有一种预感，今天会发生一些特别的事情。
EN: I have a premonition that something special will happen today.

ZH: 我的预感告诉我，这次旅行将会非常愉快。
EN: My intuition tells me that this trip will be very enjoyable.

ZH: 这个人给我一种不好的预感。
EN: This person gives me a bad premonition.

ZH: 我有一种预感，我们会在未来相见。
EN: I have a feeling that we will meet again in the future.

ZH: 我的预感告诉我，这个计划会成功。
EN: My intuition tells me that this plan will be successful.

ZH: 每当我遇到这个人，我总有一种预感要小心。
EN: Whenever I encounter this person, I always have a premonition to be careful.

ZH: 昨晚我做了一个预感成真的梦。
EN: Last night I had a dream that came true as a premonition.

ZH: 下雨的时候，我总会有一种预感。
EN: Whenever it rains, I always have a premonition.

ZH: 我有一种预感，你会取得成功。
EN: I have a feeling that you will succeed.

ZH: 那个地方给我一种神秘的预感。
EN: That place gives me a mysterious premonition.

ZH: 他对这个决定有一种预感，所以放弃了。
EN: He had a premonition about this decision, so he gave up.

ZH: 在他出发之前，他有一种预感会见到一个老朋友。
EN: Before he left, he had a premonition that he would meet an old friend.

ZH: 尽管没有证据，她相信自己的预感。
EN: Despite the lack of evidence, she believes in her premonition.

ZH: 我对这场考试有一种预感，我觉得我会成功。
EN: I have a feeling about this exam, I think I will succeed.

ZH: 每次看到这个画面，我都有一种预感。
EN: Every time I see this picture, I have a premonition.

ZH: 这首歌给我一种温馨的预感。
EN: This song gives me a warm premonition.

ZH: 他总能够凭借一种预感来找到正确的答案。
EN: He is always able to find the right answer based on a premonition.

ZH: 她有一种预感，认为他是一个可靠的人。
EN: She has a feeling that he is a trustworthy person.

ZH: 我的预感告诉我，你不会失望的。
EN: My intuition tells me that you won't be disappointed.

ZH: 尽管没有明确的迹象，但我对未来有一种预感。
EN: Despite the lack of clear signs, I have a premonition about the future.
